## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the use of emojis in digital communication. Additionally, the cultural interpretation of emojis can vary significantly, which may not be fully captured in this report. Further research could explore the evolving role of emojis in professional and cross-cultural communication contexts.

